    <item>
      <title>匈牙利工业产出暴跌凸显复苏挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/hungary-s-industry-output-plunge-underscores-recovery-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利的工业生产出现三年多前新冠疫情严重以来的最大跌幅，突显了刚从衰退中复苏的经济的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/hungary-s-industry-output-plunge-underscores-recovery-challenge</guid>
